incomprehensibly]

18:03.533 --> 18:06.500
Well, I grew Fry & Loeb
from nothing

18:06.567 --> 18:09.233
to a 100-million-dollar-a-year
firm,

18:09.300 --> 18:12.033
thanks mainly to securing
a 360 deal with Jeff's Cola.

18:12.100 --> 18:13.367
Right, right.

18:13.433 --> 18:15.233
You know, I haven't been
in the field for a while,

18:15.300 --> 18:18.000
but I've got a thick-ass
book of contacts--

18:18.067 --> 18:21.000
Niromax, P&G, Glaxo, Elron.

18:21.067 --> 18:22.100
Right.

18:22.167 --> 18:23.500
Pharmaceutical firms.

18:23.567 --> 18:25.733
Is that from your time
at Braeband?

18:25.800 --> 18:28.800
Uh, well--

18:28.867 --> 18:31.233
Didn't you do a stint
at Braeband?

18:31.300 --> 18:33.633
Yeah, but it's not
on my CV, so how--

18:33.700 --> 18:35.100
Suzy, my assistant,
used to work there.

18:35.167 --> 18:36.267
She recognized your name.

18:36.333 --> 18:38.133
Shady place, though.

18:38.200 --> 18:40.033
I've known other folk
to leave it off their CV.

18:40.100 --> 18:41.367
Well, the reason for that--

18:41.433 --> 18:43.100
It doesn't really matter.

18:43.167 --> 18:45.267
What is concerning me
right now

18:45.333 --> 18:47.200
is that you smell of alcohol.

18:49.300 --> 18:53.000
I met a friend for lunch,
and I had a beer.

18:53.067 --> 18:54.000
- But--
- You had a beer?

18:54.067 --> 18:55.367
A beer?

18:55.433 --> 18:56.600
Mate, if you had a beer,

18:56.667 --> 18:58.133
then I had lunch
with Princess Diana.

18:58.200 --> 18:59.133
You had lunch with who?

18:59.200 --> 19:00.200
Princess Diana.

19:00.267 --> 19:01.967
I'm sorry. It's--

19:02.033 --> 19:03.800
It's just very difficult
to understand you.

19:03.867 --> 19:04.867
You don't
have to understand me

19:04.933 --> 19:06.033
because you won't
be working here.

19:06.100 --> 19:08.100
Well, good, because
I don't want to work

19:08.167 --> 19:09.533
at your Scottish
whistle factory.

19:09.600 --> 19:11.467
- I'm Welsh, you idiot.
- Woo hoo!

19:11.533 --> 19:14.733
News flash. I know.
I said that to upset you.

19:14.800 --> 19:16.400
What is upsetting me
is you're still sitting here.

19:16.467 --> 19:19.633
Well, get ready to be excited
because I'm leaving.

19:19.700 --> 19:21.567
Well, you should take a good
long look at yourself mate.

19:21.633 --> 19:24.400
