a long listen to yourself,

19:24.467 --> 19:26.200
and I think you'd like
what you hear

19:26.267 --> 19:28.100
because your accent
is adorable.

19:28.167 --> 19:30.067
- I've gotta go.
- Well, don't let me stop you.

19:30.133 --> 19:32.600
I shant.
You're a cutie pie.

19:32.667 --> 19:34.233
Have a fantastic day.

19:40.067 --> 19:41.433
I don't know
why it sounded like that.

19:41.500 --> 19:44.167
I think, you know,
Kira started out of time,

19:44.233 --> 19:45.600
and then the rest followed her

19:45.667 --> 19:47.667
because she's so,
you know, developed--

19:47.733 --> 19:49.333
I mean, uh, tall.

19:49.400 --> 19:51.233
Thank you for the performance
Ms. Norris,

19:51.300 --> 19:53.633
although I didn't see
why you needed to mention
that he was gay.

19:56.100 --> 19:57.900
I'm not gonna
whitewash history.

19:57.967 --> 19:59.933
I think referencing
a teacher's sexuality,

20:00.000 --> 20:01.167
gay or straight,

20:01.233 --> 20:02.867
is inappropriate
for primary level.

20:02.933 --> 20:04.133
Really?

20:04.200 --> 20:05.900
Well, why don't you do
the next memorial, then?

20:05.967 --> 20:06.900
I'd be happy to.

20:06.967 --> 20:08.033
Great, great.

20:08.100 --> 20:09.567
Well, I hope
you don't do my memorial

20:09.633 --> 20:11.767
because I'm not ashamed
of my sexuality

20:11.833 --> 20:13.533
and I'd
want it all out there.

20:16.933 --> 20:18.567
No talking!

20:18.633 --> 20:20.333
How long do you think
it would take you

20:20.400 --> 20:22.367
to get a head teacher job?

20:22.433 --> 20:24.567
I'm never gonna get
a head teacher job.

20:24.633 --> 20:26.500
You should have seen
my assembly today.

20:26.567 --> 20:28.100
It was a car crash.

20:28.167 --> 20:29.567
Did anyone film it?

20:29.633 --> 20:31.200
What?

20:31.267 --> 20:33.767
Jesus, I fucking hope not.

