Hey.

20:43.267 --> 20:45.767
How would you feel about
putting the house on the market

20:45.833 --> 20:47.267
and getting a smaller place?

20:48.800 --> 20:51.967
Oh. Um... well--

20:52.033 --> 20:56.233
I mean, why have the pressure
of this monster mortgage?

20:56.300 --> 20:59.267
Yeah, but you're gonna
get something, right?

20:59.333 --> 21:00.600
And there's always Braeband.

21:00.667 --> 21:02.333
I mean, you can always--
I mean, Harita--

21:02.400 --> 21:04.733
Honey, I don't want
to work for those kind
of people anymore.

21:04.800 --> 21:05.833
