21:05.900 --> 21:07.467
I want to be alive
in 20 years.

21:07.533 --> 21:09.167
I want to meet
our grandchildren.

21:09.233 --> 21:10.367
Yeah, we all want that,

21:10.433 --> 21:12.133
but you've gotta
strike a balance.

21:12.200 --> 21:14.333
Of course I don't want you
to die too young,

21:14.400 --> 21:15.667
but you can't have
a stress-free job

21:15.733 --> 21:17.133
because who the fuck
are you?

21:17.200 --> 21:18.733
Why should your job
be a picnic?

21:18.800 --> 21:20.900
Kids in China are in mines.

21:20.967 --> 21:23.000
I don't care
about Chinese people.

21:23.067 --> 21:24.300
[laugh]

21:27.367 --> 21:28.633
Are you really worrying?

21:28.700 --> 21:30.000
I'm fine.

21:30.067 --> 21:31.600
Because we've got a lot
to be grateful for.

21:31.667 --> 21:33.867
You know?
You should remember that.

21:33.933 --> 21:35.367
We've got our health.

21:37.167 --> 21:38.367
You say something now.

21:38.433 --> 21:42.000
We have a beautiful,
curious, amazing daughter

21:42.067 --> 21:43.600
and Frankie.

21:44.800 --> 21:45.800
