21:54.800 --> 21:59.367
I'm trying not to,
but it's not going very well.

22:01.200 --> 22:04.300
I'm sorry your assembly
was a car crash.

22:06.167 --> 22:07.167
It's okay.

22:07.233 --> 22:09.167
I don't even really--

22:09.233 --> 22:11.233
I just wanted
to make you proud of me.

22:11.300 --> 22:13.400
