I'm sorry.
I'm sorry I shouted at you.

23:17.767 --> 23:19.333
I'm sure Wolf's a great kid.

23:19.400 --> 23:21.833
I mean, yeah, he lied
about Frankie, but so what?

23:21.900 --> 23:23.233
I mean, we're all
just doing our best.

23:23.300 --> 23:25.900
I mean, look at me.
I'm a mess.

23:25.967 --> 23:27.300
I can't provide for my family.

23:27.367 --> 23:29.400
I have diarrhea every day.

23:29.467 --> 23:33.367
You know, I have secrets
inside of me that-- Ow!

23:33.433 --> 23:34.267
Frankie!

